package.name: Apptha_Airhotels
package.summary: Airhotels Magento based script has been developed to serve the varied needs of online property rental business. This extension which is an Airbnb clone, is packed with highly advanced front-end and back-end features for the effective management of properties and reservation system. Its fluid functionality and 100% customization options makes it a highly preferable and reliable extension for rental business service providers all over the world.
